Hexadecimals to the rescue.

50:20.976 --> 50:22.211
<i>I figured one of you guys</i>

50:22.411 --> 50:24.446
<i>kept an ASCII table lying around.</i>

50:24.646 --> 50:25.747
<i>And I was right.</i>

50:25.947 --> 50:27.049
<i>Ladies and gentlemen,</i>

50:27.249 --> 50:30.620
<i>I give you super-nerd Beth Johanssen.</i>

50:30.820 --> 50:33.656
