<i>Seriously, Johanssen...</i>

50:39.595 --> 50:42.165
it's like the Smithsonian
of loneliness on there.

50:42.365 --> 50:44.267
- <i>Not that I'm complaining.</i>
- Yes!

50:44.467 --> 50:46.870
<i>Who am I to talk about loneliness?</i>

