the <i>Hermes</i> without you.

01:08:43.078 --> 01:08:46.747
<i>"We have to take turns
doing your tasks.</i>

01:08:46.948 --> 01:08:50.018
"But, I mean, it's only botany.

01:08:51.720 --> 01:08:52.787
"It's not real science."

01:08:52.987 --> 01:08:54.657
Oh, Jesus.

01:08:55.756 --> 01:08:57.158
<i>"How's Mars?"</i>

01:09:02.064 --> 01:09:05.234
<i>"Dear Martinez, Mars is fine.</i>

01:09:06.533 --> 01:09:09.370
<i>"I accidentally blew up the Hab...</i>

01:09:09.569 --> 01:09:11.305
<i>"but unfortunately,</i>

01:09:11.506 --> 01:09:16.544
